        "description": "A unified HR &amp; attendance platform used by businesses across Ghana &mdash; spanning hospitality, healthcare, education, and manufacturing. I built it end-to-end as sole developer: Time &amp; Attendance (QR / GPS / NFC clock-ins), Payroll, Leave Management, Performance Appraisals, Onboarding, Document Storage, and Multi-Branch Management. Current stack: Vue 3 admin, NestJS backend with BullMQ jobs and Redis caching, PostgreSQL, AWS S3 + GCP storage, real-time updates over WebSockets, and push via Firebase + Expo &mdash; all in a pnpm + Turborepo monorepo. Self-hosted observability stack with SigNoz + OpenTelemetry and incident alerting.",
